## First-Time Setup (Windows)

If you see errors like `'git' is not recognized` or `'pip' is not recognized`, you need to install two programs:

1. **Install Git:** https://git-scm.com/downloads/win (Use all default settings)
2. **Install Python:** https://www.python.org/downloads/ (Make sure to check **"Add Python to PATH"** )
3. **Restart** your Command Prompt

After installing, these commands will work:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/raphaelurbanek257-hub/password-strength-tester.git
cd password-strength-tester
pip install requests
python password_tester.py
